## üß∞ **Free Tools for Micro-Lesson Design**

| Tool                              | Use                                 | Notes                                    |
| --------------------------------- | ----------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------- |
| **Canva / Genially**              | Visual lesson creation              | Pre-built templates for security posters |
| **Loom / Vyond**                  | Animated micro-videos               | Fast creation of 2-min explainers        |
| **Kahoot / Quizizz**              | Interactive quizzes                 | Gamified reinforcement                   |
| **Google Forms**                  | Feedback & surveys                  | Track responses easily                   |
| **ChatGPT / Gemini**              | Script drafting & scenario creation | Fast ideation support                    |
| **Power BI / Google Data Studio** | Report dashboards                   | Visualize progress trends                |

