## üßæ **Micro-Lesson Design Checklist**

| # | Step                           | Action Required            | Owner          | Status |
| - | ------------------------------ | -------------------------- | -------------- | ------ |
| 1 | Define topic & objective       | Identify one key behavior  | Awareness Lead | ‚òê      |
| 2 | Write short story-based script | Include hook + CTA         | Content Team   | ‚òê      |
| 3 | Add visuals & narration        | Use Canva/Vyond            | Design Team    | ‚òê      |
| 4 | Test on pilot users            | Check engagement & clarity | HR / IT        | ‚òê      |
| 5 | Measure retention & report     | Use quiz + Power BI        | Analyst        | ‚òê      |

